[Enable Debug Displays [View Note]]
author=punk7890
description=*R3 + D-Pad Up = Collision Display
*R3 + D-Pad Left = CPU / DMA display
*R3 + D-Pad Right = CPU / DMA display + Collision Display
*R3 + D-Pad Down = Collision Points
*R3 + L1 = Disable HUD
*R3 + L2 = Collision Points + Disable HUD
*R3 + R2 = Everything
*L3 = Disable
patch=1,EE,D1870182,extended,0000FFEB
